.TH "ORG.BLUEZ.THERMOMETER" "5" "July 2011" "BlueZ" "Linux System Administration"
.SH NAME
org.bluez.Thermometer \- BlueZ D-Bus Health Thermometer API documentation
.SH INTERFACE
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B Service
org.bluez
.TP
.B Interface
org.bluez.Thermometer1
.TP
.B Object path
